Wombat::MamaMsgQual Class Reference

The MamaMsgQual class is a wrapper/utility class which provides useful interrogation, comparison and manipulation facilities for the Mama Message Qualifier data field (wMsgQual) which is a "bit-map" used to convey duplicate, delayed and out-of-sequence information about messages. More...

Detailed Description

The MamaMsgQual class is a wrapper/utility class which provides useful interrogation, comparison and manipulation facilities for the Mama Message Qualifier data field (wMsgQual) which is a "bit-map" used to convey duplicate, delayed and out-of-sequence information about messages.
